  "changelog": "### Stability & Hardening\n* **Speech Crash Prevention**: Wrapped monkey-patching of getPropertiesSpeech in try/except to prevent addon conflicts from crashing NVDA.\n* **Safe Property Speech**: Fixed get_property2_speech to copy states instead of mutating in-place, with try/except guard.\n* **Graceful Failure**: All monkey-patch calls (browser interceptor, speech) now fail gracefully without disrupting NVDA.\n\n### Project Cleanup\n* **Dead Files Removed**: Deleted stale localizations.json and localizations.txt.\n* **Translation Fix**: Fixed hardcoded absolute paths in messages.pot to relative paths.\n* **Documentation**: Fixed broken markdown links in README and docs.\n* **Build Pipeline**: Added GitHub Actions workflow for automated builds and releases.\n* **Gitignore**: Added comprehensive .gitignore for build artifacts and cache files.\n\n### Settings & UI\n* **Conditional Visibility**: Typing sub-options now show/hide dynamically based on the keyboard typing sound toggle.\n* **Arrow Key Navigation**: Added play navigation sounds during arrow key navigation checkbox (enabled by default). When unchecked, sounds are suppressed during arrow key navigation.\n* **Clearer Labels**: Renamed say roles to say element roles and say states to say element states.",
  "licenseURL": "https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html",
